# Generated markdown files from Quarto (.qmd -> .md)
# Pattern: Quarto posts use year/post-name/index.md, manual posts use year/post-name.md
# This ignores generated index.md in subdirectories but preserves flat .md files
src/content/blog/[0-9][0-9][0-9][0-9]/*/index.md

# Processed/moved blog images (generated by build script)
# Images from Quarto posts get moved to this year/post-name structure
# Manual images can be added directly to src/assets/images/ or other structures
src/assets/images/blog/[0-9][0-9][0-9][0-9]/*/

